### SmartAid REST tests — health & root (no auth required)
### Tool: VS Code "REST Client" extension by Huachao Mao
### Click "Send Request" above each block, or use Ctrl/Cmd+Alt+R

@host = http://localhost:3000

### 1) Root welcome
# Expected: 200 OK, { "message": "Welcome to smartAid API" }
GET {{host}}/

### 2) Health check
# Expected: 200 OK, { "message": "Server is running" }
GET {{host}}/health

### 3) Unknown route
# Expected: 404 Not Found (default Express HTML)
GET {{host}}/this-does-not-exist
